<h2 style="margin:0 0 10px 0; font-size:22px; font-weight:600;">
    ⚠️ Application No Longer Active
</h2>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:25px 0;">
    Hello {{homeBuyerName}},
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    We're writing to let you know that your mortgage application has been superseded. This typically occurs when another buyer has completed the purchase process for the same unit, or when the application has been replaced by a newer one.
</p>

<table style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:20px 0; border-collapse:collapse;">
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Application:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;"><strong>{{applicationNumber}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Property:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{propertyName}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{#if supersededDate}}
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Date:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{supersededDate}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}
</table>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    If you believe this is a mistake or would like to explore other available properties, please don't hesitate to contact us.
</p>

<a href="{{dashboardLink}}"
   style="display:inline-block; background-color:#19C2AB; color:#ffffff; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none; padding:12px 25px; border-radius:5px; margin:20px 0;">
    View Dashboard
</a>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:25px 0 10px 0;">
    We appreciate your interest and hope to assist you with your property journey.
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Best regards,<br/>
    The QShelter Team
</p>
